::Ramulus/Striker::

Ramulus shakes his head.

"We're injured, but we'll be fine. The base is just over this hi-" he stops 
midstep as they walk onto the hill, seeing the battle at the Ark.

"Not good," Striker says, transforming into his robot mode as Ramulus does 
the same. Their internal repairs have done a bit, but they were both still 
injured.

"You want to help?" Ramulus says as Striker sets off toward the Ark.
